### 发布订单测试请求
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publisherId": 1,
  "pickupCabinet": "南门一号柜",
  "targetBuilding": "学一B",
  "targetAddress": "402",
  "packageSize": 0,
  "fee": 3.50,
  "expectedTime": "2026-04-23 12:30:00",
  "remark": "轻拿轻放，别把汤洒了",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 查询跑腿大厅列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/list/hall

### 1. 准备工作：先发一个新的订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publisherId": 1,
  "pickupCabinet": "抢单测试柜",
  "targetBuilding": "实验楼",
  "targetAddress": "A101",
  "packageSize": 1,
  "fee": 10.0,
  "expectedTime": "2026-04-23 20:00:00",
  "phone": "13800000000"
}

### 2. 模拟用户 A（手速快的人）
# 注意：把这里的 orderId 换成你刚发单生成的那个 ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/accept?orderId=8&acceptorId=1001
### 3. 模拟用户 B（慢了一秒的人）
# 同样的 orderId，但 acceptorId 不同
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/accept?orderId=12&acceptorId=1002

### 测试 AI 智能发单（DeepSeek 引擎驱动）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/ai-publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "师傅帮帮忙，我有个很急的件在南门丰巢，帮我拿一下送到实验楼 A101，跑腿费我出 15 块钱，到了打我电话 13888888888。"
}

### 测试 AI 拦截提示（缺斤少两的订单）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/ai-publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "师傅，我在南门丰巢有个包裹，帮我拿到实验楼A101吧，谢啦！"
}

### 测试骑士取件（故意不传照片，预期报错 400）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/take
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 8,
  "takerId": 1001,
  "pickupPhotoUrl": ""
}

